name: CalicoMixReal
description:
CalicoMixReal takes the foundation of the CalicoMix model and enhances it with the inclusion of photorealistic elements.

With CalicoMixReal, you can delve into an anime world that is brought to life with a realistic perspective.

**Please note that you are solely responsible for any images created using this model

Recommended parameters:

This model can use the same prompt as CalicoMix but just add (8k, RAW photo, realistic, photo-realistic:1.5), for better photorealistic generation.

Recommend: (8k, RAW photo, realistic, photo-realistic:1.5), masterpiece, best quality, high resolution, extremely detailed, detailed background, cinematic lighting,

Negatives: (EasyNegative, bad-hands-5), (verybadimagenegative_v1.3), (low quality, worst quality), (missing fingers, missing hands, missing legs:1.4) (extra fingers, extra hands, extra legs:1.4), (mutate fingers, mutated hands, mutated legs:1.4), (malformed fingers:1.4), (blurry, depth of field:2.0), (poorly drawn hands, poorly drawn face), signature, watermark, logo,

CFG Scale: 6-8
*Clip skip: 2 (Very important!) ✅

Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras
Sampling steps: 20-30

Resolution: (The image composition changes with resolution.)
*recommend higher resolutions compared to standard anime generation
384x512 (not recommended): it is advised to avoid it for generating eye details as the lower resolution may result in incomplete or less satisfactory eye and face generation.
512x768 (recommended with upscaler)
768x1152 or above (recommended)
For landscape images, reverse the width and height values accordingly.

Hires fix can significantly help improve image quality.
Hires fix: R-ESRGAN 4x+
Hires step: 20
Denoising strength: 0.44

Change log:

Version 2.0:
base on CalicoMix 5.0, more stable

Version 1.0:
same as CalicoMix 3.0 + photorealistic

- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -


If you find value in this model and want to help take it to new heights,
you can support towards upgrading my GPU on Ko-fi or Buy Me a Coffee

If there's anything you need, please don't hesitate to let me know.
